      <title>根據彭博社報道，紅石和艾里森向派拉蒙投資者讓步</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/redstones-ellison-offer-concessions-paramount-investors-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據彭博社週日報道，雷石東家族和Skydance Media 執行長大衛·埃里森(David Ellison) 都做出了讓步，以使派拉蒙全球控制權的潛在變化對公司的其他投資者更具吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/redstones-ellison-offer-concessions-paramount-investors-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 01:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
